  <li id="comment-41663" class="comment odd alt thread-odd thread-alt depth-1">
    <header class="comment--meta">
      <div class="vcard"><cite class="comment-author fn"><a href="http://www.remedialeating.com" class="url" rel="ugc external nofollow">molly</a></cite></div>
      <a href="https://orangette.net/2013/12/approximately-a-soup/#comment-41663"><time class="comment-time" datetime="2013-12-06T15:06:48-05:00">Friday, December 6, 2013 at 3:06 pm</time></a>    </header>

    
    <div class="comment--content">
      <p>Three soups in a row!  Hoot!!  You have thus proved yourself a true mother.  (And three such as these?  A woman after my own heart.  Belly, really.)</p>
