      <p>I just made this with leeks and pearled barley and it was delicious. I too cut down the cooking time for the cabbage, adding the barley after about 30 minutes and then cooking everything over medium heat for another 40 minutes or so. Our 1.5 year old kept asking for tastes while the cabbage was cooking. One to add to the regular meal rotation!</p>
