  <li id="comment-41635" class="comment even thread-even depth-1">
    <header class="comment--meta">
      <div class="vcard"><cite class="comment-author fn">Amelia</cite></div>
      <a href="https://orangette.net/2013/12/approximately-a-soup/#comment-41635"><time class="comment-time" datetime="2013-12-11T23:58:45-05:00">Wednesday, December 11, 2013 at 11:58 pm</time></a>    </header>

    
    <div class="comment--content">
      <p>It feels like I&#39;m violating an unspoken taboo, deliberately cooking vegetables this long, but jeez, it&#39;s like alchemy, isn&#39;t it? </p>
<p>I used barley instead of rice, which gave the soup a nice, chewy counterpoint to the uber-tender cabbage.</p>
<p>Thank you, as always.  </p>
